e272e935c844f05ab1b2c01513217a043d62e65493c1734f8c88cc&amp;quality=70&amp;focal=2084%2C1439&amp;width=603&amp;height=339 603w, https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/6LXPSZGZRBG7XEJQO2QMDDYYDY.jpg?auth=99fc2e3909e272e935c844f05ab1b2c01513217a043d62e65493c1734f8c88cc&amp;quality=70&amp;focal=2084%2C1439&amp;width=428&amp;height=241 428w"/></div></div><div class="RectangleTeaserstyled__TeaserContentContainer-sc-123berd-1 eHXWOL"><div data-is-element-rendered="true" data-testid="teaser-content" data-teaser-size="l/m/m"><div class="Overlinestyled__Overline-sc-1jsgsl-0 kmbwpz"><span>Filmvorführung in Hohen Neuendorf</span></div><div class="TeaserContentTopstyled__HeadlineAvatarContainer-sc-9i9png-0 gAfvGj"><h2 class="Headlinestyled__Headline-sc-mamptc-0 bGMxjt TeaserContentTopstyled__Headline-sc-9i9png-1 feeylJ" data-testid="headline"><span data-testid="paid-icon-container" class="TeaserContentTopstyled__PaidIconContainer-sc-9i9png-2 kSPmPM"><div class="PaidIconstyled__PaidIcon-sc-19nr71-0 CRKtH" data-testid="PaidIcon"><svg role="img" class="PaidIconstyled__Icon-sc-19nr71-2 jVVtDZ" width="1em" height="1em" aria-labelledby="paid-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><title id="paid-icon">Kostenpflichtig</title><use xlink:href="/pf/resources/icons.svg?d=874#PlusFilledWhite"></use></svg></div>﻿</span><span>Er drehte den DDR-Sandmann und knetete die „Hoppla“-Figuren: Kameramann und Regisseur Michael Schmidt im Porträt</span></h2></div><p class="TeaserTextstyled__TeaserText-sc-1opeq3e-0 hHcBCj">Michael Schmidt aus Hohen Neuendorf hat in seinem Keller Filme und Requisiten aus seiner Zeit beim DDR-Fernsehen aufbewahrt. Er stand später bei GZSZ hinter der Kamera und traf Brad Pitt. Ein Porträt eines Mannes, der Bilder liebt.</p></div></div></article></a><div id="fusion-static-exit:contentlist-f0fiYRCWPo313Sx" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0fiYRCWPo313Sx"></div></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:f0fiYRCWPo313Sx" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0fiYRCWPo3