es-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub%2Fmadsack%2F38a58ec5-9fc7-4ebd-b8a6-a90294a8f6d4.png?auth=89cca6bcf1df7f70b49ff41981ada8ce9eafcaeaa07bc0fc457c31522c52a402&amp;quality=70&amp;width=210&amp;height=210&amp;smart=true 210w, https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fauthor-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub%2Fmadsack%2F38a58ec5-9fc7-4ebd-b8a6-a90294a8f6d4.png?auth=89cca6bcf1df7f70b49ff41981ada8ce9eafcaeaa07bc0fc457c31522c52a402&amp;quality=70&amp;width=140&amp;height=140&amp;smart=true 140w, https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fauthor-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub%2Fmadsack%2F38a58ec5-9fc7-4ebd-b8a6-a90294a8f6d4.png?auth=89cca6bcf1df7f70b49ff41981ada8ce9eafcaeaa07bc0fc457c31522c52a402&amp;quality=70&amp;width=70&amp;height=70&amp;smart=true 70w"/></div></div></div></div><div class="ArticleAuthorsListstyled__Authors-sc-2z414t-1 kOeZhB TeaserContentTopstyled__ArticleAuthorsList-sc-9i9png-3 fdxKhJ">Ein Kommentar von <!-- -->Daniela Vates</div><p class="TeaserTextstyled__TeaserText-sc-1opeq3e-0 ixmeeO">Trotz Waffenruhe und Geiselbefreiung bleibt die Lage in Nahost fragil. Als historisch könnte sich erweisen, dass US-Präsident Donald Trump plötzlich Teamwork von Staaten schätzt.</p></div></div></article></a></div></div></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:contentlist-f0f7AAr8So313rq" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0f7AAr8So313rq"></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:f0f7AAr8So313rq" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0f7AAr8So313rq"></div><div id="fusion-static-enter:f0f2fewaSo313dr" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0f2fewaSo313dr"></div><div id="fusion-static-enter:contentlist-f0f2fewaSo313dr" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0f2fewaSo313dr"></div><div id="content-list-meta-f0f2fewaSo313dr" data-testid="content-list-meta-f0f2fewaSo313dr" data-offset="2" data-ids="TCFXD5D6CRHYNF5WYOTOY6JK4U" class="ServerContentListstyled__Meta-sc-1vmrgr