er-sc-1io480m-0 hIgPBv"><img alt="" loading="lazy" sizes="70px" src="https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fauthor-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub%2Fmadsack%2Fd2be9c4f-a280-4c39-9feb-4b19ca2b69b9.png?auth=926d0592395e2061deb4d01df182a1013244d9895dce228672383e7eceded3a6&amp;quality=70&amp;width=70&amp;height=70&amp;smart=true" srcSet="https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fauthor-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub%2Fmadsack%2Fd2be9c4f-a280-4c39-9feb-4b19ca2b69b9.png?auth=926d0592395e2061deb4d01df182a1013244d9895dce228672383e7eceded3a6&amp;quality=70&amp;width=210&amp;height=210&amp;smart=true 210w, https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fauthor-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub%2Fmadsack%2Fd2be9c4f-a280-4c39-9feb-4b19ca2b69b9.png?auth=926d0592395e2061deb4d01df182a1013244d9895dce228672383e7eceded3a6&amp;quality=70&amp;width=140&amp;height=140&amp;smart=true 140w, https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fauthor-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub%2Fmadsack%2Fd2be9c4f-a280-4c39-9feb-4b19ca2b69b9.png?auth=926d0592395e2061deb4d01df182a1013244d9895dce228672383e7eceded3a6&amp;quality=70&amp;width=70&amp;height=70&amp;smart=true 70w"/></div></div></div></div><div class="ArticleAuthorsListstyled__Authors-sc-2z414t-1 kOeZhB TeaserContentTopstyled__ArticleAuthorsList-sc-9i9png-3 fdxKhJ">Ein Kommentar von  <!-- -->Markus Decker</div><p class="TeaserTextstyled__TeaserText-sc-1opeq3e-0 ixmeeO">Die Bundeswehr wird mehr Soldaten brauchen, als sich freiwillig melden dürften. Es muss also schnell geklärt werden, wie eine neue Wehrpflicht aussehen kann. Das diskutierte Losverfahren wirkt abenteuerlich - hätte aber Vorteile.</p></div></div></article></a></div></div></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:contentlist-f0f2fewaSo313dr" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0f2fewaSo313dr"></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:f0f2fewaSo313dr" style="display:n