/https%3A%2F%2Fauthor-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub%2Fmadsack%2F74597f9f-fb21-4313-91a1-28f9bbad6bcb.png?auth=9072e91878bf95e37b3a4e8e42235a1245433d3f5cd0bb974f1c9c812584e772&amp;quality=70&amp;width=70&amp;height=70&amp;smart=true 70w"/></div></div></div></div><div class="ArticleAuthorsListstyled__Authors-sc-2z414t-1 kOeZhB TeaserContentTopstyled__ArticleAuthorsList-sc-9i9png-3 fdxKhJ">Ein Kommentar von Frankreich-Korrespondentin <!-- -->Birgit Holzer</div><p class="TeaserTextstyled__TeaserText-sc-1opeq3e-0 ixmeeO">Einst galt Emmanuel Macron als politisches Wunderkind Europas. Acht Jahre später steht er als Präsident ohne Plan da und droht an seinem eigenen Machtanspruch zu zerbrechen.</p></div></div></article></a></div></div></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:contentlist-f0foVamjSo313dk" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0foVamjSo313dk"></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:f0foVamjSo313dk" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0foVamjSo313dk"></div><div id="fusion-static-enter:f0fu2spnSo313zG" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0fu2spnSo313zG"></div><div id="fusion-static-enter:contentlist-f0fu2spnSo313zG" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0fu2spnSo313zG"></div><div id="content-list-meta-f0fu2spnSo313zG" data-testid="content-list-meta-f0fu2spnSo313zG" data-offset="5" data-ids="VGAYZV43M5FQBJ4PKRQWQ3RIYE" class="ServerContentListstyled__Meta-sc-1vmrgrb-0 dVzIFK"></div><div class="SliderChainstyled__SliderChainSlide-sc-fqvmsw-9 hpMwvN"><div class="SliderChainstyled__TeaserFlexBox-sc-fqvmsw-0 bShebg"><div class="SliderChainstyled__Teaser-sc-fqvmsw-1 iozmZt"><a href="/politik/neue-e-auto-foerderung-bloss-keine-neuauflage-der-kaufpraemie-VGAYZV43M5FQBJ4PKRQWQ3RIYE.html" class="TeaserLinkstyled__Link-sc-170johp-0 bReGfB"><article class="RectangleTeaserstyled__RectangleTeaser-sc-123berd-0 hYxtXy"><div class="TeaserVariantImagestyled__TeaserVariantImage-sc-eh0uzm-0 eousYg RectangleTeaserstyl