er-sc-9i9png-2 kSPmPM"><div class="PaidIconstyled__PaidIcon-sc-19nr71-0 CRKtH" data-testid="PaidIcon"><svg role="img" class="PaidIconstyled__Icon-sc-19nr71-2 jVVtDZ" width="1em" height="1em" aria-labelledby="paid-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><title id="paid-icon">Kostenpflichtig</title><use xlink:href="/pf/resources/icons.svg?d=874#PlusFilledWhite"></use></svg></div>﻿</span><span>Zwei Tote, eine Havarie und illegale Schiffsfahrten: So lief die Saison am Berzdorfer See </span></h2></div><p class="TeaserTextstyled__TeaserText-sc-1opeq3e-0 hHcBCj">Die Badesaison am Berzdorfer See hat das Wetter schon längst beendet, jetzt endet auch die Bootssaison. Ein Angebot, das Fahrgastschiff des Unternehmers Stefan Menzel, wird es kommendes Jahr nicht mehr geben.</p></div></div></article></a><div id="fusion-static-exit:contentlist-f0fNEenG42sl5A6" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0fNEenG42sl5A6"></div></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:f0fNEenG42sl5A6" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0fNEenG42sl5A6"></div><div class="Dividerstyled__DividerSpacingVisibilityWrapper-sc-1fznxc6-0 kVsyNI"><div data-testid="divider" class="Dividerstyled__Divider-sc-1fznxc6-1 eeAvvG"> </div></div></div><div><div id="fusion-static-enter:f0f0itbU42sl5UD" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0f0itbU42sl5UD"></div><div data-testid="ContentList" class="TeaserListstyled__ContentListContainer-sc-vceyn2-0 fiUBMO"><div id="fusion-static-enter:contentlist-f0f0itbU42sl5UD" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0f0itbU42sl5UD"></div><div id="content-list-meta-f0f0itbU42sl5UD" data-testid="content-list-meta-f0f0itbU42sl5UD" data-offset="4" data-ids="VSNUOJBHVNDQ3OJNNXIGP6YIGI,QP4FNQBRK5HYJLMZDW5TKG4I7Q,5PP2UNSCMJA3BFCXYQGBGM5SG4" class="ServerContentListstyled__Meta-sc-1vmrgrb-0 dVzIFK"></div><a href="/lokales/goerlitz-lk/weisswasser/waermewende-im-kreis-goerlitz-leag-beliefert-weisswasser-bis-april-2028-mit-fernwaerme-VSNUOJBHVNDQ3OJNNXIGP6YIGI.html" class