zer/v2/BMBC462HZVHA5NPSKGCVDJTIUA.jpg?auth=ef0f6120a35395ee18a4eebcb442c2d2cd23528c9b909b8e038c1c4748ce5173&amp;quality=70&amp;focal=2540%2C1395&amp;width=428&amp;height=241 428w"/></div></div><div class="RectangleTeaserstyled__TeaserContentContainer-sc-123berd-1 eHXWOL"><div data-is-element-rendered="true" data-testid="teaser-content" data-teaser-size="l/m/m"><div class="Overlinestyled__Overline-sc-1jsgsl-0 kmbwpz"><span>Alte Scheune soll saniert werden</span></div><div class="TeaserContentTopstyled__HeadlineAvatarContainer-sc-9i9png-0 gAfvGj"><h2 class="Headlinestyled__Headline-sc-mamptc-0 bGMxjt TeaserContentTopstyled__Headline-sc-9i9png-1 feeylJ" data-testid="headline"><span data-testid="paid-icon-container" class="TeaserContentTopstyled__PaidIconContainer-sc-9i9png-2 kSPmPM"><div class="PaidIconstyled__PaidIcon-sc-19nr71-0 CRKtH" data-testid="PaidIcon"><svg role="img" class="PaidIconstyled__Icon-sc-19nr71-2 jVVtDZ" width="1em" height="1em" aria-labelledby="paid-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><title id="paid-icon">Kostenpflichtig</title><use xlink:href="/pf/resources/icons.svg?d=874#PlusFilledWhite"></use></svg></div>﻿</span><span>Tierheim Riesa: Die alten Hundezwinger haben bald ausgedient</span></h2></div><p class="TeaserTextstyled__TeaserText-sc-1opeq3e-0 hHcBCj">Noch in diesem Jahr soll die nächste Bauphase für das Tierheim auf Gut Göhlis starten. Der Chef hofft zuvor auf Unterstützung durch Handwerker.</p></div></div></article></a><div id="fusion-static-exit:contentlist-f0fc3HFIzW384lj" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="contentlist-f0fc3HFIzW384lj"></div></div><div id="fusion-static-exit:f0fc3HFIzW384lj" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0fc3HFIzW384lj"></div><div class="Dividerstyled__DividerSpacingVisibilityWrapper-sc-1fznxc6-0 kVsyNI"><div data-testid="divider" class="Dividerstyled__Divider-sc-1fznxc6-1 eeAvvG"> </div></div></div><div><div id="fusion-static-enter:f0fd44lSzW384Nn" style="display:none" data-fusion-component="f0fd44lSzW384Nn