b269143a87032a5737cca753437c776c56cb596580664d24a7d05c01240ae0&amp;quality=70&amp;focal=1765%2C1892&amp;width=767&amp;height=431 767w, https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/HO6EINMLMBBA5D2BWPWHCCZRBA.jpg?auth=e6b269143a87032a5737cca753437c776c56cb596580664d24a7d05c01240ae0&amp;quality=70&amp;focal=1765%2C1892&amp;width=603&amp;height=339 603w, https://www.saechsische.de/resizer/v2/HO6EINMLMBBA5D2BWPWHCCZRBA.jpg?auth=e6b269143a87032a5737cca753437c776c56cb596580664d24a7d05c01240ae0&amp;quality=70&amp;focal=1765%2C1892&amp;width=428&amp;height=241 428w"/></div></div><div class="RectangleTeaserstyled__TeaserContentContainer-sc-123berd-1 eHXWOL"><div data-is-element-rendered="true" data-testid="teaser-content" data-teaser-size="l/m/m"><div class="Overlinestyled__Overline-sc-1jsgsl-0 kmbwpz"><span>Eigentor entscheidet spannendes Fußball-Derby</span></div><div class="TeaserContentTopstyled__HeadlineAvatarContainer-sc-9i9png-0 gAfvGj"><h2 class="Headlinestyled__Headline-sc-mamptc-0 bGMxjt TeaserContentTopstyled__Headline-sc-9i9png-1 feeylJ" data-testid="headline"><span data-testid="paid-icon-container" class="TeaserContentTopstyled__PaidIconContainer-sc-9i9png-2 kSPmPM"><div class="PaidIconstyled__PaidIcon-sc-19nr71-0 CRKtH" data-testid="PaidIcon"><svg role="img" class="PaidIconstyled__Icon-sc-19nr71-2 jVVtDZ" width="1em" height="1em" aria-labelledby="paid-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><title id="paid-icon">Kostenpflichtig</title><use xlink:href="/pf/resources/icons.svg?d=874#PlusFilledWhite"></use></svg></div>﻿</span><span>SV Gleisberg beendet überraschend Siegesserie des Döbelner SC </span></h2></div><p class="TeaserTextstyled__TeaserText-sc-1opeq3e-0 hHcBCj">In der Fußball-Kreisoberliga Muldental/Leipziger Land sorgt der SV Gleisberg für das Ende der Ungeschlagen-Serie des Döbelner SC. Ein Eigentor entscheidet die Partie. Der Trainer spricht von einem glücklichen Triumph.</p></div></div></article></a><div id="fusion-static-exit:contentlist-f0fdmWxWax2Y24L" style="display:non